      • ItemInfo_Impl

        public ItemInfo_Impl(java.lang.String name,
                     java.awt.Image image,
                     java.awt.Point location,
                     java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> fields)
        Constructor, takes all data required about the item. An exception will be thrown if the data provided is invalid.
        Parameters:
        name - -the name/type of the item (e.g 'Chap' or 'Bug')
        image - -the image for the item
        location - -the location of the item on the board
        fields - -a map of any other fields in the item object. -the key = the name of the field as a string and the value = the value of the fields -e.g for Key this will contain: key='id', value=id(int)
